parameters.name: MaxResults
parameters.description: The number of entries per page. Valid values: 10 to 100. Default value: 50.

parameters.name: Name
parameters.description: The name of the common parameter.

parameters.name: NextToken
parameters.description: A pagination token. It can be used in the next request to retrieve a new page of results.

parameters.name: ShareType
parameters.description: The share type of the common parameter.
